videos.headline: Murray launches 75-yard pass to Brown for Sooners TD
videos.description: Kyler Murray airs it out and hits Marquise Brown in stride for a 75-yard Oklahoma touchdown.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Calcaterra loses fumble on 28-yard catch
videos.description: Grant Calcaterra makes a catch over the middle but coughs up the ball and Iowa State recovers.

videos.headline: Iowa State WR Butler will not go down on long TD
videos.description: Hakeem Butler makes a catch over the middle, breaks a few tackles and takes it 51 yards to the house for Iowa State.

videos.headline: Murray connects with Lamb for Oklahoma TD
videos.description: Kyler Murray rolls to the right and finds CeeDee Lamb for a 5-yard score to give Oklahoma the lead over Iowa State.

videos.headline: Murray's 3rd TD pass goes 5 yards to Tease
videos.description: Kyler Murray swings it out to Myles Tease, who jogs in for an easy touchdown to extend Oklahoma's lead over Iowa State.

videos.headline: Iowa State's Butler breaks away for 2nd TD catch
videos.description: Iowa State QB Zeb Noland finds Hakeem Butler down the sideline and he races 57 yards to narrow Oklahoma's lead.

videos.headline: Sermon's 22-yard TD puts Oklahoma up 2 scores
videos.description: Oklahoma's Trey Sermon jukes a defender and barrels his way into the end zone from 22 yards out vs. Iowa State.

videos.headline: Oklahoma's Sutton hurdles defender for 11-yard pickup
videos.description: Oklahoma running back Marcelias Sutton goes airborne over an Iowa State defender to pick up a few extra yards.

videos.headline: Noland's 4th down strike keeps Iowa State drive alive
videos.description: Zeb Noland finds Matthew Eaton on a 4th-and-11, leading to an Iowa State field goal later in the drive.

videos.headline: Motley INT seals Sooners' win
videos.description: Zeb Noland is pressured by the Oklahoma defense and lofts a pass that is picked off by Parnell Motley late in the fourth quarter.
